videos.description: Wake Forest's Bryant Crawford finds Doral Moore cutting down the lane for the emphatic dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Moore throws down loud two-handed dunk

videos.description: Tennessee's Admiral Schofield dishes the ball to Kyle Alexander down low for the one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Schofield sets up Alexander's slam

videos.description: Wake Forest's Mitchell Wilbekin takes it to the paint and finishes the contested layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Wilbekin sinks tough layup

videos.description: Wake Forest's Chaundee Brown picks up the loose ball and converts the tough layup for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Brown nails layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Tennessee's Kyle Alexander sets the screen for Lamonte Turner to free him for a mid-range jumper in the second half.
videos.headline: Turner knocks down mid-range jumper

videos.description: Wake Forest's Keyshawn Woods pulls up from mid-range and buries the jumper late in the first half.
videos.headline: Woods converts difficult jumper

videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bone dishes the ball to Kyle Anderson cutting to the basket for the layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Bone finds Alexander off pick and roll

videos.description: Tennessee's Derrick Walker tries finishing with a dunk but is blocked by Wake Forest's Olivier Sarr in the second half.
videos.headline: Sarr denies Walker's dunk attempt

videos.description: Tennessee's Grant Williams drives down the lane and finishes the layup despite the contact from Wake Forest's Keyshawn Woods.
videos.headline: Williams converts tough layup for and-1 chance
